{
  "stem": "22447.3",
  "chunk_idx": 13,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "At ten to 11:00, you can be sure you wouldn't see one German in the street.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There wasn't one German.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They were all off the streets.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But the inmates, they were walking about till 1, 2 o'clock in the morning.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I said, don't you know it's-- 11 o'clock is curfew?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We've been locked up long enough.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Well, I suppose you're right there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So they walked about till 1, 2 o'clock in the morning.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They had nowhere to go, nothing to do.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But the Germans, about ten till 11:00, you wouldn't see one on the road.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They're very strict on that.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Did you get involved in any way of helping other inmates?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, in the information, if they'd come in-- oh, then [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] the clothing.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "These people, they were walking about in these striped pajamas.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we had to get clothing for them.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, it was a good few miles.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was a Good few hours driving.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He went into Berlin, went into the big stores, like Harrods or Selfridges.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they just cleared the shelves.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then Montgomery's sister-- Lady Mountbatten, she was commandant of the Red Cross-- they took a big hangar where they used to keep the tanks.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they nicknamed it Harrods and started distributing the clothing, to try and clothe the people.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So I think he made two or three trips like that, to try and give somebody a pair of shoes and a dress or something to wear.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They were walking about in these pajamas.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't [? remember-- ?] till about June.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It took about a good six weeks, two months.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then one day, I was on duty in the information-- from the information desk.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "A woman came in.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
